<br />        <a name=hx20></a>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
          <tr>
          <td align="left" valign="center">
          <font size="+0" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#F52E00>
          Computer 
          &nbsp;<font color="#CCC">
          HX-20
          </font>
          </font>
          </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><td colspan=2 height=1><img src=../../../img/blank.gif width=1 height=1></td></tr>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
        </table>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
          <tr>
          <td valign=top align=left>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
The actual HX-20 computer is shown on the right.
In Japan it is known as HC-20. The com&#173;pu&#173;ter can be expanded
internally by adding a <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Read-Only Memory">ROM</span> chip, or externally by connecting
peripheral devices to the serial interfaces at the rear, or to the
parallel docking connector at the left side.
<br />
<br />
The HX-20 was available in two colours: silver and cream.
Early prototypes were reportedly dark grey or even black.
<br />
<br />
          </font></td>
          <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
          <td align=center valign=top width=100>
          <table 
           border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" ><tr><td align="center" valign=top>
<a href="img/304434/028/full.jpg">            <div style="position: relative;" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="EPSON HX-20 portable computer">
<a href="img/304434/028/full.jpg">            <div style="position: relative;" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="EPSON HX-20 portable computer">
            <img src="img/304434/028/small.jpg"
             style="
             max-width: 618px;
            "
             align="left"
             vspace="4"
             alt="EPSON HX-20 portable computer"
             border=0
             width=298 height=200
             />
            </div>
            </a>
            </td></tr><tr><td align=center>
          </td></tr></table>
          </td></tr>
