          <td valign=top align=left>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
Not yet fixed.
          </font>
          </td></tr>
        </table>
<br />        <table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
          <tr>
          <td align="left" valign="center">
          <font size="+0" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#F52E00>
          Problems
          </font>
          </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><td colspan=2 height=1><img src=../../../img/blank.gif width=1 height=1></td></tr>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
        </table>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=4>
          <tr>
          <td valign="">
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
          <ul>
            <li><s>Doesn't start BASIC</s>            <li><s>Produces only Trap! error</s>            <li>NiCd battery pack doubtful            <li>Ink cartridge worn out            <li>Rubber feet missing            <li>Cassette not running          </ul>
</font></td></tr></table>        <table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
          <tr>
          <td align="left" valign="center">
          <font size="+0" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#F52E00>
          Fixed
          </font>
          </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><td colspan=2 height=1><img src=../../../img/blank.gif width=1 height=1></td></tr>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
        </table>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=4>
          <tr>
          <td valign="">
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
          <ul>
            <li>Exterior cleaned            <li>ROMs removed and reseated            <li><a href="#rest_init">Initialisation carried out (see above)</a>          </ul>
</font></td></tr></table><div style="height: 14px;"></div>        <a name=dip></a>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
          <tr>
          <td align="left" valign="center">
          <font size="+1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#F52E00>
          <b>DIP-switch settings</b>
          </font>
          </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><td colspan=2 height=1><img src=../../../img/blank.gif width=1 height=1></td></tr>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
        </table>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
          <tr>
          <td valign=top align=left>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
The HX-20 has one <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Dual In-line Package">DIP</span>-switch consisting of 4 individual on/off switches,
located <a href="img/304434/045/full.jpg"><span data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="More about: to the left of the ROM bank">to the left of the ROM bank</span></a>
and accessible via the large <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Read-Only Memory">ROM</span>
access panel at the bottom of the device. The switches are numbered 1 to 4.
The first three switches (1-3) define which keyboard layout is used, as shown
in the table below (0 &equals; off, 1 &equals; on). Switch 4 selects the startup
medium. The <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Dual In-line Package">DIP</span>-switch in the example below is set to German (101) and starts
from the <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Beginners All Purpose Scientific Instruction Code (programming language)" data-balloon-length="large">BASIC</span> <span class="short tooltip-red" data-balloon-pos="up" aria-label="Read-Only Memory">ROM</span> (0).
          </font>
          </td></tr>
        </table>
<br />        <table border="0" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td>
        <table width=100% cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
          <tr>
          <td width=100%>
          <table
           class="table"
           width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=1 bgcolor=#FFFFFF>
            <tr>
