          </ol>
</font></td></tr></table><div style="height: 14px;"></div>        <a name=conn_rs232></a>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
          <tr>
          <td align="left" valign="center">
          <font size="+0" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#F52E00>
          RS-232 serial port
          </font>
          </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><td colspan=2 height=1><img src=../../../img/blank.gif width=1 height=1></td></tr>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
        </table>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
          <tr>
          <td valign=top align=left>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
The HX-20 has a full RS-232 port with all modem signals, brought out on
an 8-pin DIN con&#173;nec&#173;tor. The port offers a maximum speed of 4800 baud
and uses the 8N1 or 8N2 word format. Below is the pinout when looking into the socket
on the HX-20. Note that the cable shield should be connected to the shield
of the plug.
          </font>
          </td></tr>
        </table>
<br />        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=4>
          <tr>
          <td valign="">
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
          <ol>
            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">GND</div>Signal ground            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">TXD</div>Data out            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">RXD</div>Data in            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">RTS</div>Requent To Send            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">CTS</div>Clear To Send            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">DSR</div>Data Set Ready            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">DTR</div>Data Terminal Ready            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">CD</div>Carrier Detect          </ol>
          </font>
          </td>
          <td>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
          <ol>
            <table 
             border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td align="center" valign=>
              <div style="position: relative;">
              <div style="position: relative;">
              <img src="../../../ref/conn/din/svg/din8_270.svg"
