</font></td></tr></table><div style="height: 14px;"></div>        <a name=conn_ser></a>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
          <tr>
          <td align="left" valign="center">
          <font size="+0" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#F52E00>
          High speed serial port
          </font>
          </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><td colspan=2 height=1><img src=../../../img/blank.gif width=1 height=1></td></tr>
          <tr><td height=4><img src="../../../img/blank.gif" width=1 height=4></td></tr>
        </table>
        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
          <tr>
          <td valign=top align=left>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
An additional high-speed serial port is available for connection
of an external video display unit (VDU) or a floppy disk drive.
The port has a fixed speed of 38.400 baud. The pinout of the
con&#173;nector is given below. Note that the cable shield must be
connected to the shield of the plug.
          </font>
          </td></tr>
        </table>
<br />        <table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=4>
          <tr>
          <td valign="">
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
          <ol>
            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">GND</div><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">black</div>Signal ground            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">PTX</div>red            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">PRX</div>white            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">POUT</div>yellow            <li><div style="display:inline-block; width:60px;">PIN</div>green          </ol>
          </font>
          </td>
          <td>
          <font size="-1" face="Lucida Grande,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif" color=#555555>
          <ol>
            <table 
             border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td align="center" valign=>
              <div style="position: relative;">
              <div style="position: relative;">
              <img src="../../../ref/conn/din/svg/din5_180.svg"
               style="
               max-width: 618px;
              "
               align="right"
               vspace="4"
               border=0
              
